-- Bank capitalisation a key challenge for sector - Kotak Mahindra MD
-- By Neha Dasgupta
-- Fri Apr 04, 2014 02:45AM EDT
-- None



MUMBAI, April 4 (Reuters) - Bank capitalisation will be a significant challenge and constraint for Indian lenders in coming years, Kotak Mahindra Bank Ltd <KTKM.NS> Managing Director Uday Kotak said on Friday.

